<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA76">
<l>vaḻiniṉṟu niṉṉait toḻuvār vaḻuvā</l>
<l>moḻiniṉṟa mūrttiyarē yāvar – paḻutoṉṟum</l>
<l>vārāta vaṇṇamē viṇkoṭukku maṇṇaḷanta</l>
<l>cīrāṉ ṟiruvēṅ kaṭam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are steady on the way [and] worship you will be of a form</l>
<l>that stands by unfailing words . In a manner</l>
<l>that not a single mistake occurs  it gives heavens,</l> 
<l>holy Vēṅkaṭam of the Excellent one who measured the earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
